---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<BaseLayout title="Sustainability" description="Vanessa Saroni's commitment to sustainable fashion — handwoven fabrics, ethical sourcing, and minimal environmental impact.">

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="uppercase">How We Make</p>
      <h1>Sustainability</h1>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <p>We did not set out to build a sustainable brand. We set out to make beautiful things by hand. Sustainability is what happens when you do.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Vision -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <div class="vision fade-in">
        <p class="uppercase">Our Vision</p>
        <h2>Handmade Means Less Waste</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p class="vision__text">When a woman sits at a loom and weaves fabric by hand, she uses no industrial electricity, no excess water, and produces no factory waste. That is not a marketing story. That is the actual process behind every bag we make.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pillars -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-cream);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pillars fade-in">
        <div class="pillar">
          <span class="pillar__icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><path d="M12 22c4-4 8-7.5 8-12a8 8 0 1 0-16 0c0 4.5 4 8 8 12z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>We Know Every Hand</h3>
          <p>Our supply chain is short and personal. We know the women who weave our fabric. We know the workshop in Italy where our bags are assembled. Fair wages, safe conditions, real relationships.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <span class="pillar__icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>100% Handwoven</h3>
          <p>Every metre of fabric is woven by hand on a traditional loom. One day per metre. No industrial machinery, no shortcuts. The result is fabric you can feel the care in.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <span class="pillar__icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Independence Through Craft</h3>
          <p>The women who weave our fabric earn their own income, build their own skills, and strengthen their communities. Their craft is not charity. It is expertise, and we pay for expertise.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-block fade-in">
        <div class="content-block__image img-hover">
          <img src={`${base}/images/our-women-2.jpg`} alt="Artisan hand-weaving fabric in Brazil" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="content-block__text">
          <p class="uppercase">Our Mission</p>
          <h2>Designed for Years, Not Seasons</h2>
          <p>We do not follow seasonal trends. Our collections are meant to stay with you. Handwoven cotton that softens with use, Italian hardware that holds, and designs that look as good in five years as they do today.</p>
          <p>The most sustainable product is one you never throw away.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="section stats-section" style="background: var(--color-black); color: var(--color-sand);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats fade-in">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__number">100%</span>
          <span class="stat__label">Handwoven Fabrics</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__number">1 Day</span>
          <span class="stat__label">Per Metre of Fabric</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__number">0</span>
          <span class="stat__label">Industrial Machinery Used</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote -->
  <section class="quote">
    <div class="container">
      <blockquote class="fade-in">
        "I want you to choose our bags because they are beautiful, and then discover they were made the right way."
      </blockquote>
      <cite>Vanessa Saroni</cite>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .vision__text {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pillar {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillar__icon {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillar h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pillar p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .stat__number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat__label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pillars {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
